t persist across sessions. Two scopes via path prefix: /memories/project/... for repo-specific knowledge (project conventions, hard-won discoveries, dead-ends), /memories/global/... for cross-project preferences. Six commands: view, create, str_replace, insert, delete, rename. Check what's there with view /memories/project before non-trivial work; write notes ONLY when a discovery would help a future session — load-bearing facts (API quirks, conventions, counter-intuitive findings), not narrative.\\n\\nWhere in the code is the resume-signal \\\"v1 memory adoption green\\\" parsed (or is it operator-typed)?\",\"profile\":{\"id\":\"qwen3.6-35b-a3b\",\"version\":\"v3.1\",\"hash\":\"sha256:4da61fd4eec31ba079204ce43119ff39ced0ae0f1989037cc2a68c5a89c272ba\",\"path\":\"/data/projects/emmy/profiles/qwen3.6-35b-a3b/v3.1\"}}\n./runs/phase2-sc3-capture/session-2026-04-27T01-54-38-741Z.jsonl:3:{\"ts\":\"2026-04-27T01:54:38.790Z\",\"type\":\"message_end\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Where in the code is the resume-signal \\\"v1 memory adoption green\\\" parsed (or is it operator-typed)?\"}],\"timestamp\":1777254878779},\"profile\":{\"id\":\"qwen3.6-35b-a3b\",\"version\":\"v3.1\",\"hash\":\"sha256:4da61fd4eec31ba079204ce43119ff39ced0ae0f1989037cc2a68c5a89c272ba\",\"path\":\"/data/projects/emmy/profiles/qwen3.6-35b-a3b/v3.1\"}}\n./runs/phase2-sc3-capture/session-2026-04-27T01-54-38-741Z.jsonl:4:{\"ts\":\"2026-04-27T01:54:40.250Z\",\"type\":\"message_end\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"call_23cb7db272c945dab32434bf\",\"name\":\"grep\",\"arguments\":{\"pattern\":\"v1 memory adoption green\"}},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"call_8c23c3b0800449928df749bf\",\"name\":\"grep\",\"arguments\":{\"pattern\":\"memory adoption green\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"emmy-vllm\",\"model\":\"qwen3.6-35b-a3b\",\"usage\":{\"input\":2632,\"output\":58,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\